{"tid":1428822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中運動未來路向集中討論","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:32:33.000Z","uid":210336,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec6b35b2e5ea1f42face4ec6e0be82dae42d851","tid":1428822,"uid":210336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我見討論今後運動走向嘅post有啲分散，唔夠集中，所以就開咗呢個<br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭方面，何不<span style=\"color: red;\">圍困各區民政署、政府合署（嗱，市政大廈反而唔好亂掂）</span>等，恢復接公務員放工嘅行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">驚察到就be water轉場/乾脆解散，得閒又嚟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong>咁市民比較易接受</strong></span>；<br />\n<br />\n文宣與連儂牆方面，不如恢復六七月時遍地長輩圖、大規模airdrop，又加上近日新知（例如民間記者會內容、最新警察施暴），環繞五大訴求主軸，總之<span style=\"color: red;\">之前試過work嘅繼續做、停咗懶做嘅恢復</span>，點睇？呢點尤其重要，因為你警犬記者會點出醜法，都有樣嘢叫做cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw，六月嘅時候狂loop隻sing hallelujah to the lord都好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開心嘅玩法何不翻炒<br />\n<br />\n仆佢個街，越諗真係越嬲，越想清算班警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係為咗大局，大家一定要忍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddea3d075b89f2e098d2271b48b11fcb4abd79b","tid":1428822,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/8-5-北角持棍男子與示威者互毆-記者採訪遇襲-高空墮光管擊中記者頭盔/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-5-%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E6%8C%81%E6%A3%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%86-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E5%A2%AE%E5%85%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%A0%AD%E7%9B%94%2F&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=6a470601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com